des: JamFest has weekly shows that include What is Hip?! and Project Reggaeologist on Sundays. NewGrass Radio airs every Monday Night with a historic live show played on Tuesday Nights on Live Nuggets. On Wednesdays, Live From The Vault plays a full-length Classic Live Album and Thursday Night is always Festival Night on Festival Radio where JamFest plays only live music from Music Festivals. Friday Night is Club Night and the Sunday Sunday Radio Show takes us into Sunday Morning each week! JamFest is Exclusively available at Tune In. This station is a tribute to bands, songs, and artists who play at popular music festivals all over the world! A Memory of a Lifetime!
